      "id": "PopularPost316144",
      "post_content": "This is actually a pretty good option, since if your strength score is high enough you can do quite a lot. Sure, it has the downside that you're going to provoke an attack of opportunity, but the chance to immediately kill an opponent by pushing them over the edge of a cliff is difficult to pass up! A good hint, though, is to avoid using this ability on creatures that are larger than you, because they will get a hefty bonus to--  \n  \nwait.  \n  \nI seem to have made a mistake.",
